headline: Report Highlights FedEx Global Economic Impact as Company Drives Innovation
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., October 30, 2025--FedEx released its Global Economic Impact Report, highlighting its worldwide network and role in fueling innovation during its 2025 fiscal year.
